Package curam.util.client.model

Contains the view architecture of the client.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Binding
    An interface that defines the binding between a field and source and target data.
    Component
    A component is the base for all controls on a page and all of the containers for those controls.
    ComponentBuilder<C extends Component>
    A builder for components.
    ComponentParameters
    A map for parameters to components that allows default values of parameters to be retrieved when no values were explicitly set.
    Connector
    A connector represents a connection between a source path and a target path.
    Container
    A component that can contain other components.
    ContainerBuilder
    A builder for containers.
    Field
    A field represents a value to be displayed on a page or to be edited on a form.
    FieldBuilder
    A builder for Field component objects.
    Link
    A representation of a hyperlink.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComponentBuilderFactory
    A factory that creates component builders for different types of component.
    FieldParameters
    The parameters to a Field that can be used to influence the rendering of the field.
    FormItem
    A form item represents a single item in a form.
